Class ImmutableListWithDefaultValue<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.se2019.utils.ImmutableListWithDefaultValue<E>

  • public class ImmutableListWithDefaultValue<E>
extends java.lang.Object
    Implements an immutable list: once instantiated, the list cannot be modified. Also uses a default value when requesting an index not present in the list.
